predict_diagnosis:
1. Spinal muscular atrophy with respiratory distress (SMARD)
2. Metabolic myopathy with hyperammonemia and hyperhomocystinemia, such as amino acid metabolism disorder
3. Vitamin B12 deficiency-related neuropathy
4. Mitochondrial myopathy with elevated circulating creatine kinase concentration
5. Charcot-Marie-Tooth disease (CMT) with Pes cavus and decreased Achilles reflex
6. Friedreich's ataxia with hyperactive patellar reflex and distal muscle weakness
7. Myotonic dystrophy with hand muscle atrophy and abnormal tendon morphology
8. Polymyositis with proximal muscle weakness and elevated CK levels
9. Leukodystrophy with hyperhomocystinemia and vitamin B12 deficiency
10. Hereditary spastic paraplegia with talipes and abnormal pyramidal signs
